    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wixsch isdewe tam Nab-\nbagain un Behdigam Teeſu/ tad\nwinnam labbi klahjahs. Neggi\nir tas to darra manni afsiht? faſ-\nka tas KUNGS:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tawas Azzis un ta-\nwa Sirds stahw us neneeka/ ka\nween uhs to Negausibu/ un uhs\nnenoseedsigu Affins Isleejchannu/\nuhs Apbehdinachannu/ un uhs\nSadausifchannu to padarriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ta faſka tas\nKUNGS no Jojakima/ ta Deh-\nla Josijus/ ta Kehnika no Ju-\nda: Tee ne noschehlohs winnu/\n(un lazzih8:) Ak mans Brab-\nlt! ak Mahfa! tee winnu ne no-\nschehlohs: Ak Kungs! ak Zee-\nntgajs!\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ka weens Ehseltsap.\nrakts fkubst/ ta ktuhs wiſch\naprakts/ wiſch taps raustiths\nun atmests tahfu no Jerusale-\nmes Wahrtun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kaſp uhs to Lthbanu/ nn\ntauzt/ un pazellt tawu Balsi\nBalsana/ un brehz no Abari-\nma/ jo wiſſt tawi Mihletaji irr\nfatreekti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es runnaju uhs tewi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Webjsch barre-\nwiffus tawus Gannus/ nn ta-\nMihletaji ees Zeetuma/ tad ta-\nfi tu teefcham Kannā un par A-\nſineekli/ wiffas tawas Bleh-\nbas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas tu eeſch Libban-\ndsihwo/ un eeſch Zeedru-Ko-\nkein Ligsdas darri/ ka iabbi te-\nklahfees? kad few Sahves u-\nces/ Mohkas/ ka weenai/ k-\ndsemde?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tik teefcham ka es di-\nwoju/ faſka tas KUNG-\nJepfchu Kantius Jojakim\nDehts/ tas Kehnisch no Juho-\nweens speeschamajs Gredse-\nbuhtu pee mannas labbas Ro-\nkas/ tomehr gribbu es tewi-\nteunenes noraut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es nodohschu tewite-\nRohla/ kas tawu Dwehfeli m-\nle/ un teem Rohla/ pree-\nka Waiqa tu bihstees/ pro-\nNebukadnezara/ ta Kehni-\nno Babels/ nn to Kaldee-\nRohla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es ismettischu ten-\nun tawu Mahti/ kas tewi-\ndjemdejsi/ zitta Semmē/\njubs ne effeet dsimmutchi/ un-\nbuhs jums nomirt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tai Semmē/ ku-\nwinnu Dwehfeler gribbefees gr\n"
